                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <p class="lead">
                        ICST’s Founding Vision
ICST was founded to make higher education a powerful tool for breaking socio-economic barriers. Its mission is to provide accessible, job-oriented education to students from all backgrounds, particularly those with limited financial means, while promoting inclusivity and social responsibility.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Message from the Chairman – Eng. M.H.A HIRAS
Welcome to ICST University Park—a symbol of learning, innovation, and opportunity. Guided by our founder’s vision, we aim to build a vibrant academic community that values creativity, diversity, and personal growth. Together with our dedicated faculty, we are committed to fostering an enriching student experience that leaves a lasting impact on Sri Lanka’s educational landscape.

                    </p>
